Gantry-Plugins-Uaf version 0.03
===============================

This module provides an authenication and authorization framework for the 
Gantry development framework. 

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Build.PL
   ./Build
   ./Build test
   ./Build install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Gantry
  Gantry::Plugins::Cache
  Gantry::Plugins::Session

